description:
Join us at the luxury resort! After all mints, a total of 10,000 unique LuxuryPunks with rare and super-rare features will have joined the resort.

Join the luxurious community: 

https://discord.com/invite/R749uUSJQv

https://t.me/billiontoken_bll

Website:
https://luxurypunks.io/

Floor price will double at 5k and again at 7.5k mints.

Ultra-rare features include crowns, round glasses, big afros for women, high hats, smoking pipe, brown coats, pink dresses, or light-beige backgrounds. Combinations of these properties increase the rarity of LuxuryPunks significantly (e.g., round glasses + golden background)!
